(4525, '', 'pt_BR', 'question_1', '<B>1. Validade Social</B>\r\nO estudo pode contribuir para o aprimoramento cientfico e sade? Qual o potencial valor da pesquisa para cada benefcio? ', 1, 0),
(4526, '', 'en_US', 'question_1', '<B>1. Social value</B>\r\nCan the study lead to improvements in health and well-being? \r\nWhat is the potential value of the research for each of the \r\nprospective beneficiaries?', 1, 0),
(4527, '', 'es', 'question_1', '<B>1. Valor social</B>\r\nPuede el estudio mejorar la salud y el bienestar? Cul es el valor potencial de la investigacin para cada uno de los beneficiarios prospecto?', 1, 0),
(4528, '', 'fr', 'question_1', '1.	Valeur sociale Est-ce que ltude peut amliorer la sant et le bien-tre? Quelle est la valeur potentielle de cette recherche pour chacun des bnficiaires potentiels?', 1, 0),
(4529, '', 'pt_BR', 'question_2', '<B>2.Viabilidade Cientfica</B>\r\n  a investigao com metodologicamente vlida e cientificamente correta. Ser que o estudo ir gerar dados vlidos e confiveis utilizados de forma til? Ser que o desenho do estudo a se realizar contempla os objetivos cientficos, garantindo que as intervenes preservam a integridade do participante? O estudo  vivel?', 1, 0),
(4530, '', 'en_US', 'question_2', '<B>2. Scientific validity</B>\r\nIs the investigation methodologically valid and \r\nscientifically (and statistically) sound? Will the study \r\ngenerate valid and reliable data that can be generalizable \r\nand useful? Does the study design realize the scientific \r\nobjectives while guaranteeing participants the health-care \r\ninterventions to which they are entitled? Is the study \r\nfeasible?', 1, 0),
(4531, '', 'es', 'question_2', '<B>2. Validez cientfica</B>\r\nEs la investigacin metodolgicamente vlida y cientficamente (y estadsticamente) rigurosa? Generar el estudio datos vlidos y confiables que pueden ser generalizables y tiles? Realiza el diseo del estudio los objetivos cientficos al mismo tiempo que garantiza a los participantes las intervenciones en salud a las cuales tienen derecho? Es este un estudio factible?', 1, 0),
(4532, '', 'fr', 'question_2', '2. Validit scientifique: Est-ce que lenqute et son point de vue mthodologique est valable (statistiquement) et scientifiquement? Ltude fournira des donnes valables et fiables qui peuvent tre gnraliss et utiles? Est-ce que la conception de ltude  raliser les objectifs scientifiques tout en garantissant aux participants les interventions de soins de sant auxquels ils ont droit? Ltude est-elle ralisable?', 1, 0),
(4533, '', 'pt_BR', 'question_3', '<B>3. Critrios de Incluso e Excluso da amostra</B>  a populao da pesquisa selecionado para minimizar os riscos para os participantes? So participantes da pesquisa individuais selecionados para maximizar os benefcios potenciais? So os potenciais riscos e benefcios do estudo distribudos de forma justa? O estudo no pode ser realizado de outra forma?', 1, 0),
(7161, '', 'pt_BR', 'secretary_menu', 'Menu da secretaria', 1, 0),
(4534, '', 'en_US', 'question_3', '<B>3. Fair participant selection</B> What are the criteria to include and exclude participants? Is selection of participants based on scientific criteria? Is the research population selected to minimize risks to participants? Are individual research participants selected to maximize potential benefits? If participants are vulnerable, are there any safeguards to protect them? Are the risks and potential benefits of the study fairly distributed?\r\n', 1, 0),
(4535, '', 'es', 'question_3', '<B>3. Seleccin justa de participantes</B>\r\nCuales son los criterios de inclusion y exclusion de participantes? Se basa la seleccin de participantes en criterios cientficos? Se selecciona la poblacin de la investigacin para minimizer los riesgos de los participantes? Se selecciona a los participantes individuales de la investigacin para maximar los posibles beneficios? Si hay participantes vulnerables, existen salvaguardas para protegerlos de daos? Se distribuyen equitativamente los riesgos y posibles beneficios del estudio?', 1, 0),
(4536, '', 'fr', 'question_3', '3. Slection des participants quitable: Quels sont les critres pour inclure ou exclure des participants? Est-ce que la slection des participants est fonde sur des critres scientifiques? Est-ce que la population tudie est slectionne pour minimiser les risques pour les participants? Est-ce que les participants individuels de cette recherche ont t slectionns pour maximiser les avantages potentiels? Si les participants sont vulnrables, y a-t-il des garanties pour les protger? Est-ce que les risques et les avantages potentiels de ltude sont rpartis quitablement?', 1, 0),
(4537, '', 'pt_BR', 'question_4', '<B>4. Favorable risk-benefit ratio</B> Can the risks for \r\nparticipants be minimized? Can potential benefits for \r\nindividuals and society be improved? Do the potential benefits \r\nfor society and individuals outweigh the risks?', 1, 0),
(4538, '', 'en_US', 'question_4', '<B>4. Favorable risk-benefit ratio</B> Can the risks for \r\nparticipants be minimized? Can potential benefits for \r\nindividuals and society be improved? Do the potential benefits \r\nfor society and individuals outweigh the risks?', 1, 0),
(4539, '', 'es', 'question_4', '<B>4. Relacin favorable de riesgo-beneficio</B> Pueden minimizarse los riesgos para los participantes? Pueden mejorarse los posibles beneficios para los individuos y para la sociedad? Los posibles beneficios para la sociedad e individuos, sobrepasan los riesgos?', 1, 0),
(4540, '', 'fr', 'question_4', '4. Rapport bnfice/ risque favorable: Peuvent les risques tre minimiss pour les participants? Peuvent les avantages potentiels des individus et la socit tre amliore? Est-ce que les avantages potentiels pour la socit et les individus dpassent les risques?', 1, 0),
(4541, '', 'pt_BR', 'question_5', '<B>5. Informed consent</B> Is the information provided to \r\npotential participants accurate, clear, relevant and \r\ncomplete? Are the recruitment procedures, consent process \r\nand incentives appropriate for their culture and context? Is \r\nthere an appropriate plan for obtaining permission for those \r\nthat cant consent for themselves? Are the participants \r\nbeing made aware of their right to refuse to participate and \r\nare they actually free to refuse?', 1, 0),
(4542, '', 'en_US', 'question_5', '<B>5. Informed consent</B> Is the information provided to \r\npotential participants accurate, clear, relevant and \r\ncomplete? Are the recruitment procedures, consent process \r\nand incentives appropriate for their culture and context? Is \r\nthere an appropriate plan for obtaining permission for those \r\nthat cant consent for themselves? Are the participants \r\nbeing made aware of their right to refuse to participate and \r\nare they actually free to refuse?', 1, 0),
(4543, '', 'es', 'question_5', '<B>4. Consentimiento informado</B> La informacin que se prove a los posibles participantes, es exacta, clara, relevante y complete? Los procedimientos de reclutamiento, consentimiento e incentivos, son apropiados para su cultura y context? Hay un plan apropriado para obtener el permiso de aquellos que no pueden copnsentir por si mismos? Se les hace saber a los participantes sobre su derecho de rehusarse a participar y son de hecho libres de rehusarse?', 1, 0),
(4544, '', 'fr', 'question_5', '5.	Le consentement clair est linformation prcise, claire, pertinente et complte, fournie aux participants potentiels? Est- ce que les procdures de recrutement, le processus de consentement et dincitations, appropries pour leur culture et leur contexte? Y a-t-il un plan appropri pour obtenir la permission pour ceux qui ne peuvent pas donner leur consentement? Est-ce que les participants sont informs de leur droit de refuser de participer, et sont-ils rellement libre de refuser?', 1, 0),
(4545, '', 'pt_BR', 'question_6', '<B>6. Respect for participants</B> How will the health and \r\nwell-being of participants be monitored to minimize harms? \r\nHow will their privacy be protected? Can participants \r\nwithdraw from the study without penalty? What are the plans \r\nof care after the study is completed? Will participants be \r\ngiven any new information (including the results of the \r\nstudy)?', 1, 0),
(4546, '', 'en_US', 'question_6', '<B>6. Respect for participants</B> How will the health and well-being of participants be monitored to minimize harms? How will their privacy be protected? Can participants withdraw from the study without penalty? What are the plans of care after the study is completed? Will participants be given any new information (including the results of the study)?\r\n', 1, 0),
(4547, '', 'es', 'question_6', '<B>6. Respeto para con los participantes</B> Cmo se monitorear la salud y bienestar de los participantes para minimizer los daos? Cmo se proteger su privacidad? Pueden los participantes retirarse del estudio sin ninguna sancin? Cules son los planes de atencin despus que termine el estudio? Se le dar alguna nueva informacin a los participantes (incluyendo los resultados del estudio)?', 1, 0),
(4548, '', 'fr', 'question_6', '6.	Respect pour les participants: Comment est-ce que la sant et le bien-tre des participants seront contrls afin de minimiser les mfaits? Comment leur vie prive sera protge? Est-ce que les participants peuvent se retirer de ltude sans pnalit? Quels sont les plans de soins aprs ltude soit termine? Les participants recevront il toute nouvelle information (y compris les rsultats de ltude)?', 1, 0),
